@DATABASE Test.guide

@NODE Main "Script DataType - Test File 2"

@{B}Cloanto Script DataType@{UB} ą

This document is designed to be displayed with MultiView or AmigaGuide
compatible viewers.

A double-click on the "Test_2" icon executes MultiView, which in turn
tries out different DataTypes to process the "Test_2" file, which is
an AmigaDOS script programmed to display this document with a standard
Amiga viewer.

If the Script DataType is installed, this document will be displayed.
Otherwise, it is most likely that the AmigaDOS script will be displayed
as a text file.

The Script DataType enables "drag and drop" of AmigaDOS scripts such as
these test files.

Your feedback on this software is very appreciated.


